checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"大量连接错误（状态码14），描述为 'connection refused'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"与redis交互的延迟显著增加（从1361.25ms增加到11487.71ms）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 结论\n系统异常的主要原因是 `paymentservice` 无法访问，导致 `checkoutservice` 调用失败，进而引发前端服务返回HTTP 500错误。此外，`cartservice` 与 `redis` 之间的高延迟也可能加剧了问题。建议优先检查 `paymentservice` 的健康状态和网络连接。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "paymentservice is the root cause due to connection refused errors (port 50051 unreachable)"}
